Le '''Indo-Europikane chhiba''' si ekh chhibavipnaski familiya, anderyarindoi le buteder [[chhib]]a andar i [[Europa]], but andar i [[Sudutni Asiya]], [[Sudovestutni Asiya]] thai [[Mashkarutni Asiya]]. La si la o buteder gin le vakyarnengo mashkar sa le familiyande. Le [[Indo-Irane chhiba]] si i bareder Indo-Europikani rig.

==Xulavipen==
Le riga le Indo-Europikane chhibange si (rendyarde palal lengo puranipen):
*[[Anatolikane chhiba]], i puraneder jangli rig, katar o [[18to shelbersh aX]], akana muli (xasardi), anderyarindoi i chhib le [[hititurya|hititurengo]]
*[[Indo-Irane chhiba]], biyandile andar i [[Anglal Indo Irani chhib]]
**[[Indo-Ariyane chhiba]], anderyarindoi i [[Sanskrtikani]], jangle andar o mashkar le duito miebershengo
**[[Irane chhiba]], jangle andar opretele [[1000 aX]] sar i [[Avestani]], thai andar [[520 aX]] i [[Purani Persikani]]
**[[Dardikane chhiba]]
**[[Nuristane chhiba]]
*[[Elinikani (Grekikani) chhib]], i puraneder jangli si i [[Micheneyani chhib]] ([[14to shelbersh aX]])
*[[Italikane chhiba]], anderyarindoi i [[Latinikani chhib|Latinikani]] thai laki vica, le [[Romanikane chhiba]] ([[7to shelbersh aX]])
*[[Cheltikane chhiba]], Galikane lekhipena andar o [[6to shelbersh aX]]
*[[Jermanikane chhiba]], le puraneder lekhipena andar o [[2to shelbersh aX]]
*[[Armenikani chhib]], andar o [[5to shelbersh]]
*[[Toxariyane chhiba]], i muli chhib le [[Toxara|Toxarengo]], andar o [[6to shelbersh]]
*[[Balto-Slavikane chhiba]], varesave manusha phenen ke sas ekh Purani Balto-Slavikani chhib, aver phenen ke nas kadya.
**[[Slavikane chhiba]], andar o [[9to shelbersh]], le puraneder lekha pi [[Purani Khangeryaki Slavikani]]
**[[Baltikane chhiba]], andar o [[14to shelbersh]]
*[[Shkipikani chhib]] (Albanikani), andar o [[15to shelbersh]].

Avryal le kadale desh riga, sas varesave chhiba, mule vai cira jangle:

*[[Iliriyane chhiba]]
*[[Venetikane chhib]] pashal le Italikane
*[[Liburniyani chhib]] 
*[[Mesapiyani chhib]] nai jangli mishto
*[[Frijiyani chhib]], purani chhib andar i [[Frijiya]], fal te avel pashal i Elinikani, Trachikani vai Armenikani
*[[Payonyani chhib]], muli chhib ko nordo la [[Machedoniya]]ko
*[[Trachikani chhib]], fal te avel pashal i Dachikani
*[[Dachikani chhib]], fal te avel pashal i Trachikani
*[[Purani Machedonikani chhib]], fal te avel pashal i Elinikani, aver phenen ke sas pashal i Ilirikani, Trachikani vai Frijiyani
*[[Ligurikani chhib]], chi janel pes kana sas chachi Indo-Europikani, fal te avel pashal i Cheltikani

Si dudalo ke sas aver chhiba akana mule bi te janas vareso pe lende. Nai dudalo kana i [[Retikani chhib]] sas Indo-Europikani.
===Satem thai Centum chhiba===
But godyaver manusha xulaven le Indo-Europikane chhiba pe chhiba Satem vai Centum.

